Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的味噌汤是两位的闺女做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.80,0:01:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望爸爸妈妈会喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看上去就不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.13,0:01:47.77,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安 鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}妈妈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.17,0:02:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}奇怪 我不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.23,0:02:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 你在教室
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且马上就是晨会了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鹫尾 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.36,0:02:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.01,0:02:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位同学 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早安！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之轮银同学 你迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.78,0:02:29.29,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痛 很痛耶老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.52,0:02:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}赶快就座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.25,0:02:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三还是老样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小银 你今天怎么迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}升上六年级总会有不少事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忘记带课本了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.54,0:02:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天的值日生是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}起立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:03:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们能来这里 都是托神树大人的福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}向神龛敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.16,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们该完成使命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.14,0:04:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还是第一次见到呢 原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神树大人的结界？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs70\pos(394,200)\alpha&HFF&\t(0,300,0\alpha&F00&)}第{\r\blur2\fs70\alpha&HFF&\t(200,500,0\alpha&F00&)}一{\r\blur2\fs70\alpha&HFF&\t(400,700,0\alpha&F00&)}集
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(0,300,0\alpha&F00&)\move(620,480,640,500,0,400)}鹫{\r\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(200,500,0\alpha&F00&)}尾{\r\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(400,700,0\alpha&F00&)}须{\r\blur2\alpha&HFF&\t(600,900,0\alpha&F00&)}美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是神树大人做出的结界内的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}树海…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟听到的一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好壮观 全都是树耶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是大桥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概就是那个没错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连接起这里与墙壁外的桥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}敌人会从那里袭击过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好兴奋 我们竟然成了勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之轮 这可不是说着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.49,0:05:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那家伙跨过大桥 到达神树大人身边时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世界就会不复存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.83,0:05:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得由我们阻止它
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来完成使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}苍茫天地中 森罗万象拂吾身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明驻吾心 遵吾意愿现世间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}献吾之精魂 万丈神力齐相助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.31,0:05:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}献吾之精魂 承蒙圣力御外敌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的第一次实战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过我们还没有做配合训练呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为敌人出现的时间比神谕提及的更早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小心应付吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 干掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.52,0:07:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们都站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:08:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好宽敞 跟训练时完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想不到这里原本是城市
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是太奇妙了 鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.32,0:08:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从另一侧来袭的家伙 Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}击退敌人所花的时间越长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原本的世界就会受到越大的负面影响
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.03,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}速战速决
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.70,0:08:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:08:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}两位！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.84,0:09:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.04,0:09:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看我一斧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.88,0:09:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想起来这个可以当盾用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}跟强烈台风一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想想办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由我来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.06,0:10:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种敌人要怎么对付啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.04,0:10:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的弓箭伤害不够
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之轮力气不小 但难以近身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.19,0:11:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木连我都不知道怎么应付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底该如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}危险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行动起来就危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.76,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}弹性好强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}居然全喝下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是获得了神力的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把水喝干不费吹灰之力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 你好厉害 有味道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一开始是汽水 喝着喝着变成乌龙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.04,0:12:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听上去并不好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在要紧的是Vertex
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.73,0:12:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那家伙很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}分身神灵太多了 肯定离出口不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们追击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但刚才的攻击没有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但不快点 它就要跑出大桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.06,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它要是跑出去 就没办法击退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿出斗志再战一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我突然有个想法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}它发现我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}转来我们这边了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.37,0:12:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得抓紧时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.46,0:13:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这把长枪能变化成盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}园子真是万能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}顶着盾牌前进
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.13,0:13:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 撑得住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}勇者要看斗志 把它顶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来 鹫尾也跟着喊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一二 一二 一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突击
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好难瞄准
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 我把你甩过去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}尝到厉害了没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}镇魂之仪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.18,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.12,0:15:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 我狠狠地给它吃了一顿斧头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多亏有你 仪式开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}平息下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.18,0:15:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}击退…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.08,0:16:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来我们不会直接回学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟了 还穿着室内鞋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚才拍到树海了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 照片不是树海了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.41,0:16:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看来是拍不下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}喂 鹫尾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}须美？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}须美助？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.15,0:16:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是险胜而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.63,0:16:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果只有我一个人 就输定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.58,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\fs30\1c&H545454&\frx356\fry6\frz5.832\pos(250,296)}【没有朋友】如何与人交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.58,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H545454&\frz5.832\pos(272,398)\frx356\fry2}「没有朋友…」这个烦恼很让人难受吧。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.58,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord0\b0\fs20\1c&H545454&\frx356\fry2\pos(308,600)\frz6.678}我来教你几招交朋友的诀窍吧♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.58,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn华康黑体W7\bord2\b0\fs30\1c&H6938F2&\3c&HFFFFFF&\frx356\fry2\frz6.678\pos(344,646)}3{\shad2\bord2\1c&HC6DAD9&\3c&H3B4C4F&\4c&H3B4C4F&}大妙招
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:16:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}昨天也跟各位同学说过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这三位同学肩负着神树大人指派的重要使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以她们会像昨天那样 突然从教室消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到时候不要慌张慌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}静下心来 默默为她们三个加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同学们还是要以平日的课业为重
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.67,0:17:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}使命很辛苦吗 受了伤很痛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可不能告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小气鬼～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:29.08,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}告诉我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木 三之轮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可以的话…我们去开个庆功宴…好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.42,0:17:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:18:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…我对平安迎来今天 感到由衷的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这美好的一天我宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神世纪298年 勇者初战告捷庆功宴正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}祝在座的各位身体健康 学业有成 前途无量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:19.20,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太死板了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.27,0:18:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你 须美助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.49,0:18:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我之前也好几次想邀请你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.56,0:18:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以超开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是鹫尾第一次主动邀请我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}确实如此呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}都还没配合演练过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我们第一场战斗打得真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也很兴奋 有好多想说的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是 想要和你们说说话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以邀请了你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我以前不是很信任你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并不是说我讨厌你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是我不习惯依赖他人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}须美助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.91,0:19:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但这样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}如果…只有我一个人 肯定什么都办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为有你们在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…所以我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.00,0:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我能跟你们当朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们不是已经是了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好开心 我也好想和须美助当朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.57,0:19:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实我也不太会交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来须美助的想法跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好开心呀 须美助
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…乃木
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么突然用须美助叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知不觉就帮你取了个绰号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你自己都没自觉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.62,0:20:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}高兴是高兴啦 但我不太喜欢这个绰号呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.82,0:20:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那鹫娜怎么样 很有偶像的感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}更不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃木也不喜欢「园琳琳」这种叫法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起 当我没说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想到了 你觉得「鹫鹫」怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就这样吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请多指教 鹫鹫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.58,0:20:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 那你们就叫我银吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.42,0:21:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「三之轮」听上去好见外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来庆祝交上朋友的今天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家一起去吃这里超赞的冰淇淋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.04,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}选择焙茶‧可尔必思口味太对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}三三你的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}酱油蚕豆口味
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.61,0:21:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那是什么口味 不过看上去挺好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抹茶淡淡的苦编织出的口味 真是绝妙的搭配
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.41,0:21:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么好吃的话 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.55,0:21:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种事我是第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好吃 这就是第一次配合工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.55,0:21:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用词很会让人想歪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早就想跟朋友做一次这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鹫鹫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好开心呀
Comment: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,OP-FF FINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:19.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}キミを連れて駆け出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:22.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}誰も追いつけない場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:27.70,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}今こそ叶えようよ　あの日のやくそく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:42.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}片隅の幸せのつぼみ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.50,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}銀色に輝いた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:48.65,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}咲いたら見せてあげよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:53.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}見返したアルバムの中で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:56.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}その頃も今もそう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.92,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}一緒に笑ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:04.71,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}南のほうから染まっていく季節
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:07.30,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}ただいまと言ってね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.30,0:23:10.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}きっとすぐに迎えに行く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:13.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}キミを連れて駆け出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:15.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}誰も追いつけない場所へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:20.97,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}今こそ叶えようよ　あの日のやくそく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:26.18,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}ねえ　ずっと待ってたよ　キミのことを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:32.82,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}おかえり　私をもう二度と置いてかないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.90,0:22:19.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}牵起你的手 迈开脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:22.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}去那片没有人能够追上的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:27.70,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}让我们在这里 实现那一天许下的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:42.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}吐露在角落里的 一株幸福的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}闪耀着银露的光泽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.50,0:22:48.65,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}等它绽放 就让我带你来看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.83,0:22:53.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}翻来覆去过的这本相册
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.51,0:22:56.40,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}记录着那个时候 还有今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:22:58.92,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}我们纯真的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:04.71,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}南方吹来的春风 为世界染上了绿意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.71,0:23:07.30,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}记得说声「我回来了」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.30,0:23:10.39,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}我一定三步并作两步迎接你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.39,0:23:13.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}牵起你的手 迈开脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:15.72,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}去那片没有人能够追上的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:20.97,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}让我们在这里 实现那一天许下的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.97,0:23:26.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}你知道吗 我一直等待着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:32.82,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur5}欢迎回来 可不要再丢下我独自启程
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神世纪298年 这是三位勇者交织成的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:23:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是被神明选中的少女们谱写的童话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.92,0:24:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明选中的 总是天真无邪的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而在大多数情况下 少女们的结局会是—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.39,0:24:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要举例就是战舰长门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.24,0:24:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.80,0:24:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太古怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:19.96,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}突击
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.06,0:24:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}玩真心话大冒险‧喜欢的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有园子在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.56,0:24:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回家前都是合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.35,0:24:26.32,BackGround,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}终点！
